beer.beer_description:
J.A.C.K. is one of our first beer we brewed in our brewery. Josefine, Anders, Chris and Kalle did a pretty good job, eh? And the best thing? It's sessionable but still with a lot of flavours. Win win!

Malt: Maris Otter Pale Ale and Light Crystal. 

Hos: Simcoe and Citra 

FOOD PAIRINGS: Seafood,Indian spices, cuts through fatty dishes such as battered fish.
